P_HTM[203]="*Sattannaṃ āpattikkhandhānaṃ katamo āpattikkhandho?**To which of the seven classes of offenses does it belong?*";
P_HTM[204]="*Channaṃ āpattisamuṭṭhānānaṃ katihi samuṭṭhānehi samuṭṭhāti?**Through how many of the six kinds of origins of offenses does it originate?*";
