P_HTM[655]="*Kismiṃ vatthusminti?**“What is it about?”*";
P_HTM[656]="*Āyasmā udāyī aññātikāya bhikkhuniyā purāṇacīvaraṃ dhovāpesi, tasmiṃ vatthusmiṃ.**Udāyī having an unrelated nun wash a used robe.*";
