P_HTM[658]="*Channaṃ āpattisamuṭṭhānānaṃ chahi samuṭṭhānehi samuṭṭhāti …pe….**Of the six kinds of origins of offenses, it originates in six ways: …*";
P_HTM[659]="*Aññātikāya bhikkhuniyā hatthato cīvaraṃ paṭiggaṇhantassa nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ kattha paññattanti?**“The offense entailing relinquishment and confession for receiving a robe directly from an unrelated nun—where was it laid down?”*";
