P_HTM[714]="*Kismiṃ vatthusminti?**“What is it about?”*";
P_HTM[715]="*Chabbaggiyā bhikkhū kosiyakārake upasaṅkamitvā evamāhaṃsu “bahū, āvuso, kosakārake pacatha.**Those monks going to the silk-makers and saying, “Please boil a heap of silkworms*";
P_HTM[716]="*Amhākampi dassatha.**and give us silk.*";
