P_HTM[1235]="*Channaṃ āpattisamuṭṭhānānaṃ catūhi samuṭṭhānehi samuṭṭhāti …pe….**Of the six kinds of origins of offenses, it originates in four ways: …*";
P_HTM[1236]="*Adinnaṃ mukhadvāraṃ āhāraṃ āharantassa pācittiyaṃ kattha paññattanti?**“The offense entailing confession for eating food that has not been given—where was it laid down?”*";
