P_HTM[1240]="*Kismiṃ vatthusminti?**“What is it about?”*";
P_HTM[1241]="*Aññataro bhikkhu adinnaṃ mukhadvāraṃ āhāraṃ āhari, tasmiṃ vatthusmiṃ.**That monk eating food that had not been given.*";
