P_HTM[1269]="*Channaṃ āpattisamuṭṭhānānaṃ ekena samuṭṭhānena samuṭṭhāti—**Of the six kinds of origins of offenses, it originates in one way:*";
P_HTM[1270]="*kāyato ca cittato ca samuṭṭhāti, na vācato …pe….**from body and mind, not from speech. …*";
