P_HTM[1288]="*kāyato ca cittato ca samuṭṭhāti, na vācato …pe….**from body and mind, not from speech. …*";
P_HTM[1289]="*Nimantitena sabhattena santaṃ bhikkhuṃ anāpucchā purebhattaṃ pacchābhattaṃ kulesu cārittaṃ āpajjantassa pācittiyaṃ kattha paññattanti?**“The offense entailing confession for being invited to a meal and then visiting families beforehand or afterwards without taking leave of an available monk—where was it laid down?”*";
