P_HTM[2869]="*Dukkaṭaṃ.**an offense of wrong conduct.*";
P_HTM[2870]="*Anādariyaṃ paṭicca harite uccāraṃ vā passāvaṃ vā kheḷaṃ vā karonto ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjati.**When, out of disrespect, one defecates, urinates, or spits on cultivated plants, one commits one kind of offense:*";
P_HTM[2871]="*Dukkaṭaṃ.**an offense of wrong conduct.*";
P_HTM[2872]="*Anādariyaṃ paṭicca udake uccāraṃ vā passāvaṃ vā kheḷaṃ vā karonto kati āpattiyo āpajjati?**When, out of disrespect, one defecates, urinates, or spits in water, how many kinds of offenses does one commit?*";
P_HTM[2873]="*Anādariyaṃ paṭicca udake uccāraṃ vā passāvaṃ vā kheḷaṃ vā karonto ekaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjati.**When, out of disrespect, one defecates, urinates, or spits in water, one commits one kind of offense:*";
P_HTM[2874]="*Dukkaṭaṃ—**an offense of wrong conduct.*";
