P_HTM[4459]="*“Alaṃ tāva te, ayye, vuṭṭhāpitenā”ti vuccamānāya “sādhū”ti paṭissuṇitvā pacchā khīyanadhammaṃ āpajjantiyā pācittiyaṃ kattha paññattanti?**“The offense entailing confession for verbally consenting when being told, “Venerable, you have given enough full admissions for now,” but then criticizing it afterwards—where was it laid down?”*";
