P_HTM[4467]="*Sikkhamānaṃ—“sace me tvaṃ, ayye, cīvaraṃ dassasi, evāhaṃ taṃ vuṭṭhāpessāmī”ti vatvā neva vuṭṭhāpentiyā na vuṭṭhāpanāya ussukkaṃ karontiyā pācittiyaṃ kattha paññattanti?**“The offense entailing confession for telling a trainee nun, “Venerable, if you give me a robe, I’ll give you the full admission,” but then neither giving her the full admission nor making any effort to have her fully admitted—where was it laid down?”*";
P_HTM[4468]="*Sāvatthiyaṃ paññattaṃ.**At Sāvatthī.*";
P_HTM[4469]="*Kaṃ ārabbhāti?**“Whom is it about?”*";
