P_HTM[4649]="*Chattupāhanavaggo navamo.**The ninth sub-chapter on sunshades and sandals is finished.*";
P_HTM[4650]="*Navavaggakhuddakā niṭṭhitā.**The section on minor rules in nine sub-chapters is finished.*";
P_HTM[4651]="*Tassuddānaṃ**This is the summary:*";
P_HTM[4652]="*Lasuṇaṃ saṃhare lomaṃ,**“Garlic, hair from the private parts,*";
P_HTM[4653]="*talamaṭṭhañca suddhikaṃ;**Palm, dildo, cleaning;*";
P_HTM[4654]="*Bhuñjantāmakadhaññānaṃ,**Eating, of raw grains,*";
P_HTM[4655]="*dve vighāsena dassanā.**Two with food scraps, seeing.*";
P_HTM[4656]="*Andhakāre paṭicchanne,**In the dark, concealed,*";
P_HTM[4657]="*ajjhokāse rathikāya ca;**Out in the open, and on a street;*";
P_HTM[4658]="*Pure pacchā vikāle ca,**Before, after, and at the wrong time,*";
P_HTM[4659]="*duggahi niraye vadhi.**Misunderstanding, invoking hell, beat.*";
P_HTM[4660]="*Naggodakā visibbetvā,**Naked, bathing, unstitched,*";
P_HTM[4661]="*pañcāhikaṃ saṅkamanīyaṃ;**Five days, borrowed;*";
P_HTM[4662]="*Gaṇaṃ vibhaṅgasamaṇaṃ,**Group, distribution, monastic,*";
P_HTM[4663]="*dubbalaṃ kathinena ca.**Uncertain, and with the robe-making season.*";
P_HTM[4664]="*Ekamañcattharaṇena,**With the same bed, and with the same sheet,*";
P_HTM[4665]="*sañcicca sahajīvinī;**Intentionally, disciple;*";
P_HTM[4666]="*Datvā saṃsaṭṭhaanto ca,**Giving, socializing, and within,*";
P_HTM[4667]="*tirovassaṃ na pakkame.**Outside, rainy season, should she not go.*";
P_HTM[4668]="*Rājā āsandi suttañca,**Royal, couch, and yarn,*";
P_HTM[4669]="*gihi vūpasamena ca;**Householder, and with resolving;*";
P_HTM[4670]="*Dade cīvarāvasathaṃ,**Should give, robe, lodging,*";
P_HTM[4671]="*pariyāpuṇañca vācaye.**And studying, should she teach.*";
P_HTM[4672]="*Ārāmakkosacaṇḍī ca,**Monastery, abusing, and enraged,*";
P_HTM[4673]="*bhuñjeyya kulamaccharī;**Should she eat, stingy with families;*";
P_HTM[4674]="*Vāse pavāraṇovādaṃ,**Should she spend, invitation, instruction,*";
P_HTM[4675]="*dve dhammā pasākhena ca.**Two things, and with the thigh.*";
P_HTM[4676]="*Gabbhī pāyantī cha dhamme,**A pregnant woman, a breastfeeding woman, six rules,*";
P_HTM[4677]="*asammatūnadvādasa;**One who has not been approved, less than twelve;*";
P_HTM[4678]="*Paripuṇṇañca saṅghena,**And more than twelve, by the Sangha,*";
P_HTM[4679]="*saha vuṭṭhā cha pañca ca.**Disciple, admission, and five or six.*";
P_HTM[4680]="*Kumārī dve ca saṅghena,**An unmarried girl, and two, by the Sangha,*";
P_HTM[4681]="*dvādasa sammatena ca;**Twelve, and with one who has been approved;*";
P_HTM[4682]="*Alaṃ sace ca dvevassaṃ,**Enough, and if, for two years,*";
P_HTM[4683]="*saṃsaṭṭhā sāmikena ca.**Socializing, and by the husband.*";
P_HTM[4684]="*Pārivāsikānuvassaṃ,**Expired, every year,*";
P_HTM[4685]="*duve vuṭṭhāpanena ca;**And with the admission of two;*";
P_HTM[4686]="*Chattayānena saṅghāṇi,**Sunshade, in a vehicle, hip ornament,*";
P_HTM[4687]="*itthālaṅkāravaṇṇake.**Jewellery, with colors.*";
P_HTM[4688]="*Piññākabhikkhunī ceva,**Oil-seed flour, and a nun,*";
P_HTM[4689]="*sikkhā ca sāmaṇerikā;**And a trainee nun, a novice nun;*";
P_HTM[4690]="*Gihi bhikkhussa purato,**A female householder, in front of a monk,*";
P_HTM[4691]="*anokāsaṃ saṅkaccikāti.**Not permission, a chest wrap.”*";
P_HTM[4692]="*Tesaṃ vaggānaṃ uddānaṃ**This is the summary of the sub-chapters:*";
P_HTM[4693]="*Lasuṇandhakārā nhānā,**“Garlic, the dark, bathing,*";
P_HTM[4694]="*tuvaṭṭā cittagārakā;**Lying down, pleasure house;*";
P_HTM[4695]="*Ārāmaṃ gabbhinī ceva,**Monastery, and pregnant women,*";
P_HTM[4696]="*kumārī chattupāhanāti.**Unmarried girls, sunshades and sandals.”*";
