P_HTM[6319]="*Sattannaṃ āpattikkhandhānaṃ katihi āpattikkhandhehi saṅgahitā?**In how many of the seven classes of offenses are they found?*";
P_HTM[6320]="*Channaṃ āpattisamuṭṭhānānaṃ katihi āpattisamuṭṭhānehi samuṭṭhanti?**Through how many of the six kinds of origins of offenses do they originate?*";
