P_HTM[6689]="*sativinayo, amūḷhavinayo, paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ, tassapāpiyasikā, tiṇavatthārako.**resolution through recollection, resolution because of past insanity, acting according to what has been admitted, further penalty, and covering over as if with grass.*";
