P_HTM[7017]="*14. Samathādhikaraṇavāra**14. The section on principles for settling and legal issues*";
P_HTM[7018]="*Samathā samathehi sammanti?**Are principles for settling settled through principles for settling?*";
P_HTM[7019]="*Samathā adhikaraṇehi sammanti?**Are principles for settling settled through legal issues?*";
P_HTM[7020]="*Adhikaraṇā samathehi sammanti?**Are legal issues settled through principles for settling?*";
P_HTM[7021]="*Adhikaraṇā adhikaraṇehi sammanti?**Are legal issues settled through legal issues?*";
P_HTM[7022]="*Siyā samathā samathehi sammanti, siyā samathā samathehi na sammanti.**It may be that principles for settling are settled through principles for settling; it may be that principles for settling are not settled through principles for settling.*";
P_HTM[7023]="*Siyā samathā adhikaraṇehi sammanti, siyā samathā adhikaraṇehi na sammanti.**It may be that principles for settling are settled through legal issues; it may be that principles for settling are not settled through legal issues.*";
P_HTM[7024]="*Siyā adhikaraṇā samathehi sammanti, siyā adhikaraṇā samathehi na sammanti.**It may be that legal issues are settled through principles for settling; it may be that legal issues are not settled through principles for settling.*";
P_HTM[7025]="*Siyā adhikaraṇā adhikaraṇehi sammanti, siyā adhikaraṇā adhikaraṇehi na sammanti.**It may be that legal issues are settled through legal issues; it may be that legal issues are not settled through legal issues.*";
P_HTM[7026]="*Kathaṃ siyā samathā samathehi sammanti, kathaṃ siyā samathā samathehi na sammanti?**How may it be that principles for settling are settled through principles for settling? And how may it be that principles for settling are not settled through principles for settling?*";
P_HTM[7027]="*Yebhuyyasikā sammukhāvinayena sammati;**(a) A majority decision is settled through resolution face-to-face.*";
P_HTM[7028]="*sativinayena na sammati, amūḷhavinayena na sammati, paṭiññātakaraṇena na sammati, tassapāpiyasikāya na sammati, tiṇavatthārakena na sammati.**It is not settled through resolution through recollection, through resolution because of past insanity, through acting according to what has been admitted, through further penalty, or through covering over as if with grass.*";
P_HTM[7029]="*Sativinayo sammukhāvinayena sammati;**(b) Resolution through recollection is settled through resolution face-to-face.*";
P_HTM[7030]="*amūḷhavinayena na sammati, paṭiññātakaraṇena na sammāti, tassapāpiyasikāya na sammati, tiṇavatthārakena na sammati, yebhuyyasikāya na sammati.**It is not settled through resolution because of past insanity, through acting according to what has been admitted, through further penalty, through covering over as if with grass, or through majority decision.*";
P_HTM[7031]="*Amūḷhavinayo sammukhāvinayena sammati;**(c) Resolution because of past insanity is settled through resolution face-to-face.*";
P_HTM[7032]="*paṭiññātakaraṇena na sammati, tassapāpiyasikāya na sammati, tiṇavatthārakena na sammati, yebhuyyasikāya na sammati, sativinayena na sammati.**It is not settled through acting according to what has been admitted, through further penalty, through covering over as if with grass, through majority decision, or through resolution through recollection.*";
P_HTM[7033]="*Paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ sammukhāvinayena sammati;**(d) Acting according to what has been admitted is settled through resolution face-to-face.*";
P_HTM[7034]="*tassapāpiyasikāya na sammati, tiṇavatthārakena na sammati, yebhuyyasikāya na sammati, sativinayena na sammati, amūḷhavinayena na sammati.**It is not settled through further penalty, through covering over as if with grass, through majority decision, through resolution through recollection, or through resolution because of past insanity.*";
P_HTM[7035]="*Tassapāpiyasikā sammukhāvinayena sammati;**(e) A further penalty is settled through resolution face-to-face.*";
P_HTM[7036]="*tiṇavatthārakena na sammati, yebhuyyasikāya na sammati, sativinayena na sammati, amūḷhavinayena na sammati, paṭiññātakaraṇena na sammati.**It is not settled through covering over as if with grass, through majority decision, through resolution through recollection, through resolution because of past insanity, or through acting according to what has been admitted.*";
P_HTM[7037]="*Tiṇavatthārako sammukhāvinayena sammati;**(f) Covering over as if with grass is settled through resolution face-to-face.*";
P_HTM[7038]="*yebhuyyasikāya na sammati, sativinayena na sammati, amūḷhavinayena na sammati, paṭiññātakaraṇena na sammati, tassapāpiyasikāya na sammati.**It is not settled through majority decision, through resolution through recollection, through resolution because of past insanity, through acting according to what has been admitted, or through further penalty.*";
P_HTM[7039]="*Evaṃ siyā samathā samathehi sammanti.* **";
P_HTM[7040]="*Evaṃ siyā samathā samathehi na sammanti.* **";
P_HTM[7041]="*Kathaṃ siyā samathā adhikaraṇehi sammanti, kathaṃ siyā samathā adhikaraṇehi na sammanti?**How may it be that principles for settling are settled through legal issues? How may it be that principles for settling are not settled through legal issues?*";
P_HTM[7042]="*Sammukhāvinayo vivādādhikaraṇena na sammati, anuvādādhikaraṇena na sammati, āpattādhikaraṇena na sammati;**(a) Resolution face-to-face is not settled through a legal issue arising from a dispute, a legal issue arising from an accusation, or a legal issue arising from an offense.*";
