P_HTM[8613]="*Niyassakammassa paṭippassaddhiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the lifting of a legal procedure of demotion?*";
P_HTM[8614]="*Pabbājanīyakammassa paṭippassaddhiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the lifting of a legal procedure of banishment?*";
P_HTM[8615]="*Paṭisāraṇīyakammassa paṭippassaddhiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the lifting of a legal procedure of reconciliation?*";
P_HTM[8616]="*Ukkhepanīyakammassa paṭippassaddhiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the lifting of a legal procedure of ejection?*";
P_HTM[8617]="*Sativinayassa ko ādi, kiṃ majje, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of resolution through recollection?*";
P_HTM[8618]="*Amūḷhavinayassa ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of resolution because of past insanity?*";
P_HTM[8619]="*Tassapāpiyasikāya ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of a further penalty?*";
P_HTM[8620]="*Tiṇavatthārakassa ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of covering over as if with grass?*";
P_HTM[8621]="*Bhikkhunovādakasammutiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of appointing an instructor of the nuns?*";
P_HTM[8622]="*Ticīvarena avippavāsasammutiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the permission to stay apart from one’s three robes?*";
P_HTM[8623]="*Santhatasammutiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of a blanket-permission?*";
P_HTM[8624]="*Rūpiyachaḍḍakasammutiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of appointing a money discarder?*";
P_HTM[8625]="*Sāṭiyaggāhāpakasammutiyo ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of appointing a distributor of rainy-season bathing cloths?*";
P_HTM[8626]="*Pattaggāhāpakasammutiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of appointing a distributor of almsbowls?*";
P_HTM[8627]="*Daṇḍasammutiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the permission to use a staff?*";
P_HTM[8628]="*Sikkāsammutiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the permission to use a carrying-net?*";
P_HTM[8629]="*Daṇḍasikkāsammutiyā ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānaṃ?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the permission to use a staff and a carrying-net?*";
P_HTM[8630]="*2 Ādimajjhantavissajjanā**2. Replies on the beginning, the middle, and the end*";
P_HTM[8631]="*Uposathakammassa ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānanti?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the observance-day procedure?*";
P_HTM[8632]="*Uposathakammassa sāmaggī ādi, kiriyā majjhe, niṭṭhānaṃ pariyosānaṃ.**A complete assembly is the beginning of an observance-day procedure, carrying it out is the middle, and concluding it is the end.*";
P_HTM[8633]="*Pavāraṇākammassa ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānanti?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of the invitation procedure?*";
P_HTM[8634]="*Pavāraṇākammassa sāmaggī ādi, kiriyā majjhe, niṭṭhānaṃ pariyosānaṃ.**A complete assembly is the beginning of an invitation procedure, carrying it out is the middle, and concluding it is the end.*";
P_HTM[8635]="*Tajjanīyakammassa ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānanti?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of a legal procedure of condemnation?*";
P_HTM[8636]="*Tajjanīyakammassa vatthu ca puggalo ca ādi, ñatti majjhe, kammavācā pariyosānaṃ.**The action that is the basis for the offense and the person who has done it are the beginning of a procedure of condemnation, the motion is the middle, and the announcement is the end.*";
