P_HTM[8645]="*Abbhānassa vatthu ca puggalo ca ādi, ñatti majjhe, kammavācā pariyosānaṃ.**The action that is the basis for the offense and the person who has done it are the beginning of rehabilitation, the motion is the middle, and the announcement is the end.*";
P_HTM[8646]="*Upasampadākammassa ko ādi, kiṃ majjhe, kiṃ pariyosānanti?**What is the beginning, the middle, and the end of an ordination procedure?*";
