P_HTM[8732]="*124. 1. Sattanagaresupaññattasikkhāpada **124.  1. Training rules laid down in seven towns *";
P_HTM[8733]="*“Ekaṃsaṃ cīvaraṃ katvā,**“Putting your robe over one shoulder,*";
P_HTM[8734]="*paggaṇhitvāna añjaliṃ;**Raising your joined palms—*";
P_HTM[8735]="*Āsīsamānarūpova,**What are you hoping for*";
P_HTM[8736]="*kissa tvaṃ idha māgato”.**That you have come here?”*";
P_HTM[8737]="*“Dvīsu vinayesu ye paññattā,**“What has been laid down in the two Monastic Laws,*";
P_HTM[8738]="*Uddesaṃ āgacchanti uposathesu;**That comes up for recitation on the observance days—*";
P_HTM[8739]="*Kati te sikkhāpadā honti,**How many training rules do they have?*";
P_HTM[8740]="*Katisu nagaresu paññattā”.**In how many towns were they laid down?”*";
P_HTM[8741]="*“Bhaddako te ummaṅgo,**“Your approach is excellent,*";
P_HTM[8742]="*yoniso paripucchasi;**You question sensibly;*";
P_HTM[8743]="*Taggha te ahamakkhissaṃ,**And so I will tell you,*";
P_HTM[8744]="*yathāsi kusalo tathā”.**According to your skill.*";
P_HTM[8745]="*“Dvīsu vinayesu ye paññattā,**What has been laid down in the two Monastic Laws,*";
P_HTM[8746]="*Uddesaṃ āgacchanti uposathesu;**That comes up for recitation on the observance days—*";
P_HTM[8747]="*Aḍḍhuḍḍhasatāni te honti,**They are three hundred and fifty,*";
P_HTM[8748]="*Sattasu nagaresu paññattā”.**Laid down in seven towns.”*";
P_HTM[8749]="*“Katamesu sattasu nagaresu paññattā,**“In which seven towns were they laid down?*";
P_HTM[8750]="*Iṅgha me tvaṃ byākara naṃ;**Please tell me this;*";
P_HTM[8751]="*Taṃ vacanapathaṃ nisāmayitvā,**And after attending carefully to your explanation,*";
P_HTM[8752]="*Paṭipajjema hitāya no siyā”.**We will practice for our own benefit.”*";
P_HTM[8753]="*“Vesāliyaṃ rājagahe,**“They were laid down at Vesālī, Rājagaha,*";
P_HTM[8754]="*sāvatthiyañca āḷaviyaṃ;**At Sāvatthī, Āḷavī;*";
P_HTM[8755]="*Kosambiyañca sakkesu,**And at Kosambī, and among the Sakyans,*";
P_HTM[8756]="*bhaggesu ceva paññattā”.**And also among the Bhaggas.”*";
P_HTM[8757]="*“Kati vesāliyaṃ paññattā,**“How many were laid down at Vesālī?*";
P_HTM[8758]="*kati rājagahe katā;**How many were pronounced at Rājagaha?*";
P_HTM[8759]="*Sāvatthiyaṃ kati honti,**How many were there at Sāvatthī?*";
P_HTM[8760]="*kati āḷaviyaṃ katā”.**How many were pronounced at Āḷavī?*";
P_HTM[8761]="*“Kati kosambiyaṃ paññattā,**How many were laid down at Kosambī?*";
P_HTM[8762]="*kati sakkesu vuccanti;**How many were spoken among the Sakyans?*";
P_HTM[8763]="*Kati bhaggesu paññattā,**How many were laid down among the Bhaggas?*";
P_HTM[8764]="*taṃ me akkhāhi pucchito”.**Please tell me who have asked.”*";
P_HTM[8765]="*“Dasa vesāliyaṃ paññattā,**“Ten were laid down at Vesālī,*";
P_HTM[8766]="*Ekavīsa rājagahe katā;**Twenty-one pronounced at Rājagaha;*";
P_HTM[8767]="*Chaūna tīṇisatāni,**And two hundred and ninety-four*";
P_HTM[8768]="*Sabbe sāvatthiyaṃ katā.**Pronounced at Sāvatthī.*";
P_HTM[8769]="*Cha āḷaviyaṃ paññattā,**Six were laid down at Āḷavī,*";
P_HTM[8770]="*aṭṭha kosambiyaṃ katā;**Eight pronounced at Kosambī;*";
P_HTM[8771]="*Aṭṭha sakkesu vuccanti,**Eight spoken among the Sakyans,*";
P_HTM[8772]="*tayo bhaggesu paññattā.**And three laid down among the Bhaggas.*";
