P_HTM[9098]="*vipatti caturopi ca;**And also the four kinds of failure;*";
P_HTM[9099]="*Bhikkhūnaṃ bhikkhunīnañca,**In common, not in common*";
P_HTM[9100]="*sādhāraṇā asādhāraṇā;**Between the monks and the nuns.*";
P_HTM[9101]="*Sāsanaṃ anuggahāya,**To support the Instruction,*";
