P_HTM[9351]="*Yattha paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ tattha sammukhāvinayo?**When there is acting according to what has been admitted, is there also resolution face-to-face?*";
P_HTM[9352]="*Yattha sammukhāvinayo tattha paṭiññātakaraṇaṃ?**When there is resolution face-to-face, is there also acting according to what has been admitted?*";
P_HTM[9353]="*Yattha yebhuyyasikā tattha sammukhāvinayo?**When there is a majority decision, is there also resolution face-to-face?*";
P_HTM[9354]="*Yattha sammukhāvinayo tattha yebhuyyasikā?**When there is resolution face-to-face, is there also a majority decision?*";
P_HTM[9355]="*Yattha tassapāpiyasikā tattha sammukhāvinayo?**When there is a further penalty, is there also resolution face-to-face?*";
