P_HTM[9430]="*Sattannaṃ samathānaṃ kati mūlāni, kati samuṭṭhānā?**How many sources do the seven principles for settling legal issues have, and how many origins?*";
P_HTM[9431]="*Sattannaṃ samathānaṃ chabbīsa mūlāni, chattiṃsa samuṭṭhānā.**They have twenty-six sources and thirty-six origins.*";
P_HTM[9432]="*Sattannaṃ samathānaṃ katamāni chabbīsa mūlāni?**What are those twenty-six roots?*";
P_HTM[9433]="*Sammukhāvinayassa cattāri mūlāni—**Resolution face-to-face has four roots:*";
P_HTM[9434]="*saṅghasammukhatā, dhammasammukhatā, vinayasammukhatā, puggalasammukhatā;**face-to-face with the Sangha, face-to-face with the Teaching, face-to-face with the Monastic Law, face-to-face with the persons concerned.*";
