P_HTM[11361]="*Vinidhāya diṭṭhiṃ kammena,**“He misrepresents his view during the legal procedure,*";
P_HTM[11362]="*uddese voharena ca;**During the recitation, and while he speaks;*";
P_HTM[11363]="*Anussāvane salākena,**During the proclamation, during the voting—*";
P_HTM[11364]="*pañcete diṭṭhinissitā;**These five are dependent on view;*";
P_HTM[11365]="*Khantiṃ ruciñca saññañca,**Belief, and acceptance, and perception—*";
P_HTM[11366]="*tayo te pañcadhā nayāti.**These three by the fivefold method.”*";
P_HTM[11367]="*12. Dutiyasaṅghabhedakavagga**12. The second sub-chapter on schism in the Sangha*";
