P_HTM[12472]="*Vīsativaggakaraṇe kamme vīsati bhikkhū pakatattā kammapattā, avasesā pakatattā chandārahā.**In regard to a a legal procedure that requires group of twenty, twenty regular monks should be present and for the remainder of regular monks it is proper to give their consent.*";
